synopsis.value: Ketheric sits silently on a raised throne, watching with cold eyes as Minthara defends herself and her failure to capture the artefact. Behind her are a gaggle of goblins, including Sazza, who are shifting uncomfortably as she throws them under the bus. They are surrounded by guards. Disciple Z'Rell seems to be in charge of "the prosecution". The player enters and moves to the front of the spectators before a guard stops them.
